Haris Vuckic has been loaned to Rangers from Newcastle on a season-long deal . 
  The Slovenia international admits he is uncertain over his future after 12 months at St James' Park . 
  He is one of five Newcastle players on loan at Ibrox . 
  The 22-year-old has scored six goals in 10 games for the Gers . 
  He says Rangers would be a 'good option' if Newcastle let him leave . 
  Vucksic has 12 months left on his Newcastle deal . 
 